{"tid":1356370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［預左俾人屌］你地咁樣發洩有咩用？革命係要用理性架","createTime":"2019-07-23T13:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T14:10:26.000Z","uid":204385,"like":27,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"290be3f1c34b1deb367c6158da3782d6677b7fee","tid":1356370,"uid":204385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"唔好再理咩何妖達哥，個啲野根本唔重要。<br />\n少少花邊新聞就搞到你地班連登仔失哂焦。<br />\n<br />\n我無足夠既智慧去判斷應唔應該搞元朗，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正因為咁先更加要把握時間討論</span><br />\n<br />\n革命係要用理性去商討戰略、諗下一步既對策。唔係係度打下飛機就得，我地依家仲係未贏過呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地班連登仔咁樣對得住個6位戰友同無數被捕既手足咩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該唔好再推無聊post，將焦點放返去下一步既文宣、對策同行動，做實事，當我求下大家。"},{"pid":"f92bab81b1e0d973e4173e07f03877eb357e6048","tid":1356370,"uid":204385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:17:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"86f3a41ff05fe00d27e2f4b6f0d6cfaca1a9d9ef","tid":1356370,"uid":204385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f6800b512bc6227e0616e258e83db87dfd819804","tid":1356370,"uid":217757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:19:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3edf3ec52002e78d2f3a05709b65a89c3589891","tid":1356370,"uid":204385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:19:41.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"28ce5c2aa4861e2fd2ade7bc0f52537f763efce5","tid":1356370,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:20:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"274af0c773b6d3a0608a58451f061dec01d062b1","tid":1356370,"uid":204385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"五大訴求呢"},{"pid":"8202bdccc2e6e71b896054400702b05c7420664e","tid":1356370,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13906e205283d212b6deca446cb0b